net.proteusframework.data.filesystem

Class FileSystemEntityNameComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.FileSystemEntityNameComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<FileSystemEntity>

    public class FileSystemEntityNameComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<FileSystemEntity>
    Compares FileSystemEntity objects by name. This implementation will also compare database ID if the names are equal which allows it to be used in a TreeSet or similar type of sorted collection.
